{"tid":1632234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略 / 國際線 + 後續考慮] 停止幫中資裝修 專心拆鐵同星期二死城","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:57:03.000Z","uid":133495,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39a8d376a25b7ea45ce2ada3e34839ecc7da1274","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">零。</span></span><br />\n呢篇係基於外國勢力同民主法案既考慮。以上兩點有幾重要我諗我唔再解釋。TLDR既睇紅字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一。停止裝修</span></span><br />\n裝修成本當然係低，基本上集中喺後線，無警情況下進行，只再blackbloc做得好就零風險。就係因為太容易做個個都加一腳，市面上九成既360吉野家美心已經裝修過，之後就轉到中銀、中移，再之後點？我明呢啲開咗個頭好難停，但唔難想像之後範圍擴大至所有中資。<br />\n事實上大部分香港商鋪都中資，滙豐老麥都係。我哋唔係唔出聲就唔打咩，<span style=\"color: red;\">對藍絲藍鋪我哋都係還手，唔係主攻，就算佢紅底，只要佢無對示威者出言不遜，就忍忍手先。重點係文宣好快跟唔上喇</span>，如果有「中國」兩個字就打，同中國之前反日有咩分別，見Toyota Honda就打。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喺外國人面前我哋一定要做弱者！</span><br />\n如果你覺得唔靠外國勢力，淨係燒鋪就贏到中共既，請你再諗清楚啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">二。點解要拆鐵</span></span><br />\n岩岩講咁多，點解拆鐵又ok？係因為拆咗成個月，外國一早已經明白哂，而<span style=\"color: red;\">人民VS黨鐵真係有機會贏！</span>18區任拆已經令到佢地修復唔切同無零件。<span style=\"color: red;\">另外鐵對社會打擊最大</span>，而三個月嚟我哋就係想做到呢點。冇鐵就冇得翻工，要翻工就要塞車。無鐵既話，大部分公司已經等同罷工，有助星期二死城。而且拆鐵無咁易TK，點燒點拆，都唔影響市民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">三。點解死城</span></span><br />\n第一，<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非出場，勇武補血</span>，最簡單既一環，就係乜都唔做，留係屋企就可以抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n第二，喺國際新聞上洗太平地。政府緊急法後，全城熄機，民不聊生，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人做翻弱者，用一日時間喺國際間拎翻個新聞重點，用文宣洗版。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四。後續</span></span><br />\n我知點講都好聽日都會有人出手，出手之前諗吓，有冇助星期二罷工。到星期二，就諗有冇助星期三......<span style=\"color: red;\">總之就係以最低武力癱瘓個城市，令傳媒、甚至自己唔好失焦。</span>"},{"pid":"4dd863be8fb65c2fd5ae71159a55a0fc29daac2f","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105468d4d2746c1dcb0ee9a712e55cd3f62d33bf","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060a6c023b3d8e8979004c0dc895a827c0a67d4","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2ab9757aa8644684120bb2de522a9f89ef48e0","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dab361bc4ac4b0f3f21266ed0241f4cbccc134f","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b47c3c00299684ef7f318f30f06d98ba31e119","tid":1632234,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse